OL,3,CMabel the missing dog is found dead
OL,4,Cafter fears she was stolen for breeding
OL,6,FA Lancashire family say they are
OL,7,Fheartbroken after their beloved cocker
OL,8,Fspaniel, who's been missing for 3
OL,9,Fmonths has been found dead.
OL,11,FMabel, an 18-month-old Cocker Spaniel,
OL,12,Fwas last seen at the farm in Inskip on
OL,13,Fthe morning of Friday the 10th of
OL,14,FApril.
OL,16,FHer owners, Sarah and Paul Livesey
OL,17,Ffear a visitor to their farm shop may
OL,18,Fhave stolen her for breeding. They put
OL,19,Fup a #10,000 reward for her safe
OL,20,Freturn but have now revealed the sad
OL,21,Fnews of her death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
