OL,3,CMabel the missing dog is found dead
OL,4,Cafter fears she was stolen for breeding
OL,6,FSarah described her as "the most
OL,7,Floving loyal dog, she is literally the
OL,8,Fcentre of our family."
OL,10,FBeauty's Legacy - a charity
OL,11,Fspecialising in reuniting lost and
OL,12,Fstolen pets - were brought in to help
OL,13,Fsearch for her, they posted on their
OL,14,FFacebook page:
OL,16,F"It is with the heaviest of hearts we
OL,17,Fannounce that Mabel's body has been
OL,18,Ffound.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
