OL,3,CMabel the missing dog is found dead
OL,4,Cafter fears she was stolen for breeding
OL,6,FSarah and her family are absolutely
OL,7,Fbroken, they did everything they could
OL,8,Fto find their girl.
OL,10,FMay we take this opportunity to thank
OL,11,Feveryone for all your help and hard
OL,12,Fwork. This has devastated the team,
OL,13,Fand we know many of you who have been
OL,14,Fso invested will feel heartbroken.
OL,15,FFeel free to contact our charity for
OL,16,Fany support you may need."
OL,18,FLancashire Police are investigating.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
