OL,3,CMabel the missing dog is found dead
OL,4,Cafter fears she was stolen for breeding
OL,6,FIt is believed around 2,000 dogs are
OL,7,Fstolen in the UK every year with the
OL,8,FNorth West one of the highest risk
OL,9,Fareas.
OL,11,FStealing a dog is now a specific
OL,12,Fcriminal offence and perpetrators can
OL,13,Fbe jailed for up to five years.
OL,15,FLisa Eardley, centre manager at the
OL,16,FDogs Trust Manchester, said: "I don't
OL,17,Fthink they consider the impact it has
OL,18,Fon families when they steal these dogs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
