OL,3,CMabel the missing dog is found dead
OL,4,Cafter fears she was stolen for breeding
OL,6,F"It's an easy way to make money and
OL,7,Fit's quite quick and you can move dogs
OL,8,Fquite quickly and sadly this is the
OL,9,Freality we are in at the moment,
OL,10,Fespecially with what we call 'cute
OL,11,Fbreeds'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
